{{Quote|It has been a long while since I saw Wuitho Trifalls. I visited there with my family the week before I went off to the Imperial Academy. NovaCom maintained a repulsorlift cabin in the area, so that's where we stayed. It was as beautiful as that picture, but without the roar of the water, it seems&hellip;|Tycho Celchu|<ref name="X-Wing: Wedge's Gamble">''[[X-Wing: Wedge's Gamble]]''</ref>}}
'''Wuitho Trifalls''' was a [[River (disambiguation)|river]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] which fell in three spectacular waterfalls. [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]] and his family visited there a [[Standard week|week]] before he went to the [[Imperial Naval Academy/Legends|Imperial Academy]]. [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] had a [[Hologram/Legends|hologram]] of the falls in his quarters on [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]].

